#

Roasted Garlic Guacamole

30 min
$6.5
240 kcal
Difficulty: 15%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackHealthy

Description

A creamy and flavorful twist on classic guacamole, enriched with the sweetness of roasted garlic.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • roasted garlic cloves: 4
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh cilantro: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
